# Nabledge-6 Knowledge Index

# PROTOTYPE: L2+title hint design (Issue #88)
# This file contains a PROTOTYPE of the new hint design for 8 entries.
# The new design uses L2 (technical components) + title (Japanese + English) only,
# removing L1 (generic domain terms) and L3 (functional terms).
# L3 keywords are moved to .index sections in knowledge files.
#
# Format change:
#   OLD: title, L1 L2 L3, path
#   NEW: title, L2 title_ja title_en, path
#
# Example (ユニバーサルDAO):
#   OLD: ユニバーサルDAO, データベース DAO O/Rマッパー CRUD JPA 検索 ページング 排他制御, ...
#   NEW: ユニバーサルDAO, DAO O/Rマッパー CRUD JPA ユニバーサルDAO UniversalDao, ...
#
# Changes:
#   - Removed L1: データベース (too generic, causes noise)
#   - Removed L3: 検索 ページング 排他制御 (moved to .index in knowledge file)
#   - Added title: ユニバーサルDAO UniversalDao (improves recall for direct title matches)
#
# English Title Conventions:
# - PascalCase for class/component names: UniversalDao, DatabaseAccess, SessionStore
# - Clear word boundaries in compounds: JDBCWrapper (not Jdbcwrapper)
# - Match official Nablarch naming where possible
# - Use common English terms for concepts: Transaction, Validation, Handler

